sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor A as Admin<br/>(one-time setup)
    participant SF as Salesforce<br/>External Credential Principal
    participant DB as Dropbox<br/>(login, consent & API)
    participant X as Apex<br/>(runtime)
    participant N as Named Credential<br/>Engine

    Note over A,DB: PART 1 — one time: connect the account
    A->>SF: Click "Authenticate" on the principal
    SF->>DB: Browser opens — Dropbox login<br/>+ consent screen (scopes listed)
    DB-->>SF: authorization code → tokens<br/>access + refresh, stored encrypted

    Note over X,N: PART 2 — runtime: every callout afterwards
    X->>N: callout:Dropbox_API/2/files/list_folder
    N->>N: Access token expired?<br/>Refresh silently with the refresh token
    N->>DB: Request + Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;
    DB-->>N: 200 OK — JSON
    N-->>X: HttpResponse

    Note over A,N: Humans consent once — machines run forever after
